* Newland, Samuel J. &quot;The National Guard: Whose Guard Anyway?&quot; &quot;The US Army War College Quarterly: Parameters&quot; 18.1 (1988): 32+ online
* Todd, Frederick P. &quot;Our National Guard: An Introduction to its History.&quot; &quot;Military Affairs: Journal of the American Military Institute&quot; (1941): 152-170.

