===Argentina===
*H-91 - CH-47C on display at the Museo Nacional de Aeronáutica de Argentina in Morón, Buenos Aires.

===Australia===
*A15-104 - CH-47D on display at the Australian Army Flying Museum in Oakey, Queensland.

===Canada===
